{"id":8119,"date":"2018-07-31T15:59:47","date_gmt":"2018-07-31T10:29:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=8119"},"modified":"2022-12-23T16:49:17","modified_gmt":"2022-12-23T11:19:17","slug":"reham-khan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/reham-khan\/","title":{"rendered":"Reham Khan Wiki, Age, Husband, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8142\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"541\" height=\"541\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 541px) 100vw, 541px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Reham Khan<\/strong> is a <strong>journalist<\/strong>, <strong>Television presenter<\/strong>, and a <strong>producer<\/strong> from <strong>Pakistan<\/strong>. She is famous for being the second and <strong>ex-wife of the former Pakistani cricketer and politician &#8216;Imran Khan<\/strong>.&#8217;\u00a0Check out Reham Khan Wiki, Height, Weight, Age, Husband, Family, Biography &amp; More.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-8158\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"487\" height=\"487\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-1.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-1-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 487px) 100vw, 487px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce37e62904\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce37e62904\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/reham-khan\/#BiographyWiki\" title=\"Biography\/Wiki\">Biography\/Wiki<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/reham-khan\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/reham-khan\/#Family_Husband\" title=\"Family, Husband\">Family, Husband<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/reham-khan\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/reham-khan\/#Controversies\" title=\"Controversies\">Controversies<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/reham-khan\/#Facts\" title=\"Facts\u00a0\">Facts\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BiographyWiki\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Biography\/Wiki<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Reham Khan is <strong>49 years<\/strong> old Pakistani media person who was born on <strong>3 April 1973<\/strong> at\u00a0<strong>Ajdabiya<\/strong>, <strong>Libya<\/strong> in a highly educated family. She spent her childhood at\u00a0Baffa, Mansehra District, Khyber-Pukhtoonkhwa, Pakistan. She completed her schooling from <strong>Presentation Convent School<\/strong>, <strong>Peshawar<\/strong> and later graduated in <strong>B. Ed.<\/strong> from <strong>Jinnah College for Women<\/strong>, <strong>Peshawar<\/strong>. She claims that she has a post-graduate degree in <strong>broadcast media<\/strong> from <strong>Grimsby Institute, North East Lincolnshire, England<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-5.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-8163\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"524\" height=\"393\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-5.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-5-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-5-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-4.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-8161\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"452\" height=\"466\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-4.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-4-291x300.jpg 291w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Physical Appearance<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Reham is a beautiful Pakistani journalist who has a quite good height of <strong>5&#8242; 7&#8243; inches<\/strong>, and she weighs around <strong>55 kg<\/strong>. She looks quite fit and slim despite crossing the 40. Her eyes and hair both are black.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-2.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-8159\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"445\" height=\"560\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-2.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-2-239x300.jpg 239w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 445px) 100vw, 445px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-3.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-8160\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"458\" height=\"709\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-3.jpg 517w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-3-194x300.jpg 194w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 458px) 100vw, 458px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family_Husband\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Family, Husband<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Reham belongs to a well-educated and well-reputed family from Baffa, Pakistan. Her father name is <strong>Nayyar Ramzan<\/strong> who was a physician and mother name is <strong>Saeeda Nayyar<\/strong> who is quite close to Reham.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8153\" style=\"width: 380px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Mother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8153\" class=\" wp-image-8153\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Mother.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"370\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Mother.jpg 422w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Mother-254x300.jpg 254w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8153\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan With Her Mother<\/p><\/div>\n<p>She has an elder sister named <strong>Salma Nayyar<\/strong> and a brother named <strong>Munir Khan Nayyar<\/strong>. Reham follows the <strong>Islam<\/strong> as her family does, and her ethnicity is <strong>Pashtun<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8155\" style=\"width: 403px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Sister-Salma.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8155\" class=\" wp-image-8155\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Sister-Salma.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"393\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Sister-Salma.jpg 480w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Sister-Salma-232x300.jpg 232w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 393px) 100vw, 393px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8155\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan Sister Salma<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Reham married her first cousin\u00a0<strong>Ejaz-ur-Rehman<\/strong> (a psychiatrist) in <strong>1992<\/strong> and they both blessed with three children. She has a son named\u00a0<strong>Sahir Rehman<\/strong> and two daughters named\u00a0<strong>Inaya Rehman<\/strong> and <strong>Ridha Rehman<\/strong>.\u00a0They both separated in <strong>2006<\/strong> due to some family issues.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8175\" style=\"width: 525px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-First-Ex-Husband-Ejaz-ur-Rehman.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8175\" class=\" wp-image-8175\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-First-Ex-Husband-Ejaz-ur-Rehman.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"515\" height=\"386\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-First-Ex-Husband-Ejaz-ur-Rehman.jpg 640w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-First-Ex-Husband-Ejaz-ur-Rehman-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 515px) 100vw, 515px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8175\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan With Her First Ex-Husband Ejaz-ur-Rehman<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_8154\" style=\"width: 573px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Children.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8154\" class=\"wp-image-8154\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Children.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"563\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Children.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Children-300x214.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Children-768x547.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8154\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan With Her Children<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_8149\" style=\"width: 437px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khans-Daughter.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8149\" class=\" wp-image-8149\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khans-Daughter.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"427\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khans-Daughter.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khans-Daughter-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khans-Daughter-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khans-Daughter-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 427px) 100vw, 427px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8149\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan&#8217;s Daughter\u00a0Inaya<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_8148\" style=\"width: 433px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Son-Sahir.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8148\" class=\" wp-image-8148\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Son-Sahir.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"423\" height=\"423\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Son-Sahir.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Son-Sahir-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Son-Sahir-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Her-Son-Sahir-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 423px) 100vw, 423px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8148\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan With Her Son Sahir<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Later, on<strong> 6 January 2015<\/strong>, she married famous <strong>Pakistani cricketer and politician &#8216;Imran Khan&#8217;<\/strong> but they both separated within a\u00a0year of their marriage.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8156\" style=\"width: 566px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Imran-Khan.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8156\" class=\" wp-image-8156\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Imran-Khan.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"556\" height=\"393\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Imran-Khan.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Imran-Khan-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Imran-Khan-768x542.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8156\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan With Imran Khan<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In December 2022, she took to Twitter to announce her third marriage with a US-based Pakistani actor and satirist named Mirza Bilal in the US city of Seattle. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_8119_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_8119_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_8119_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_8119_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_8119_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ndtv.com\/world-news\/imran-khans-ex-wife-reham-khan-marries-us-based-actor-3632241\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">NDTV<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_136458\" style=\"width: 373px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-with-Mirza-Bilal.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-136458\" class=\" wp-image-136458\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-with-Mirza-Bilal.jpg\" alt=\"Reham Khan with Mirza Bilal\" width=\"363\" height=\"601\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-with-Mirza-Bilal.jpg 483w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-with-Mirza-Bilal-181x300.jpg 181w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 363px) 100vw, 363px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-136458\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan with Mirza Bilal<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Career<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Reham started working as a media person after the separation with her ex-husband\u00a0Ejaz-ur-Rehman in 2006. She joined the <strong>Legal TV<\/strong> and started working as a lead <strong>Television presenter<\/strong>. Later, in 2007, she moved to the\u00a0<strong>Sunshine Radio Hereford &amp; Worcester<\/strong> and worked as a\u00a0<strong>\u201cBreakfast News Presenter\u201d<\/strong> for one year. In 2008, she joined the <strong>BBC<\/strong> and worked as a <strong>weather presenter<\/strong> and with the time, she became the senior journalist at the same channel. After working for a few years at BBC, she went back to her country Pakistan and joined the big fishes of Pakistani media and worked for them. She also tried her luck in the entertainment industry and made her debut as a producer with the film Janaan in 2016.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-6.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-8165\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-6.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-6-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-6-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversies\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Controversies<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>After her divorce from her first husband, Ejaz-ur-Rehman, she claimed that she faced domestic violence during her first marriage. While Ejazur rubbished her claims and said that she is just trying to destroy his reputation to gain sympathy.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She claims that she has a postgraduate degree in broadcast media from the North Lindsey College, England. But, in 2015, a British newspaper conveyed that the college denied enrolling any student by the name \u201cReham Khan,\u201d that proves that degree is fake.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>On 12 July 2018, she launched her autobiography titled &#8220;Reham Khan&#8221; and made several shocking revelations about various personalities. As a consequence, she received many legal notices from businessman Sayed Zulfikar Bukhari, her ex-husband Imran Khan, Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf Foreign Media Head Anila Khawaja, and psychiatrist Ejaz-ur-Rehman, for defaming them.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Facts\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Facts\u00a0<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Reham was born into a well-reputed family of Baffa village, Pakistan. She belongs to the Swati tribe.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Her father, Nayyar Ramzan and her paternal uncle, Abdul Hakeem Khan both were well-educated and renowned personalities from Baffa village. Her father was a Physician and a doctorate\u00a0degree holder. Her paternal uncle was a Justice and governor of the North-West Frontier Province (NWFP).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>When she was just 19 years old, she did an arrange marriage to\u00a0Ejaz-ur-Rehman who was 14 years older than her. Later, they both settled down in England.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>They both separated in 2006 and the same year Reham started working at the Legal TV. Later, she also worked with media houses like\u00a0Sunshine Radio Hereford &amp; Worcester and BBC.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><iframe title=\"Reham Khan Morning Weather BBC South Off Disc\" width=\"1060\" height=\"795\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/Hng3N0jc3Fg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Her most memorable interview was with Badam Zari, the first female contested for elections independently from the Federally Administered Tribal Areas (FATA) in Bajaur.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2013, Reham went back to her country Pakistan and worked with big media houses such as Dawn TV, PTV, Neo TV, News One, Aaj TV, and In Focus.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In January 2015, she married Imran Khan who was 20 years older than her but the same year they both separated.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She is a foodie and loves to taste a variety of cuisines. She also loves cooking, Travelling, and Doing Social Work.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_8171\" style=\"width: 502px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Food-Lover.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8171\" class=\" wp-image-8171\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Food-Lover.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"492\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Food-Lover.jpg 656w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Food-Lover-300x274.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8171\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan A Food Lover<\/p><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>She is fluent in\u00a0English, Urdu, Hindko, and Pashtu.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She is an avid dog lover.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_8170\" style=\"width: 387px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-A-Dog-Lover.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8170\" class=\" wp-image-8170\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-A-Dog-Lover.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"377\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-A-Dog-Lover.jpg 440w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-A-Dog-Lover-236x300.jpg 236w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 377px) 100vw, 377px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8170\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan A Dog Lover<\/p><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>Her Ex-husband, Imran Khan, was once interested in elder sister, Salma Nayyar, in the 1990s.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Her favourite foods are Backing Cupcakes, Gol Gappe, Sushi, Pizza, and Tiramisu.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She runs an organization to protect and educate the Pakistani children.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_8168\" style=\"width: 464px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Organisation.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8168\" class=\" wp-image-8168\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Organisation.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"454\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Organisation.jpg 621w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-Organisation-300x290.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8168\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan Organisation<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_8169\" style=\"width: 469px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Children.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8169\" class=\" wp-image-8169\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Children.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"459\" height=\"459\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Children.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Children-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Children-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Reham-Khan-With-Children-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 459px) 100vw, 459px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-8169\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reham Khan With Children<\/p><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>Her favourite actor is Shah Rukh Khan.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Her salary is\u00a0\u00a345053 p. a.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She drinks alcohol.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_8119_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_8119_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)